\## Blocking Issues (Must Fix Before Approval)



1\. \*\*Remove and Rotate Credentials\*\*

&#x20;  - Delete .env from repository

&#x20;  - Add .env to .gitignore

&#x20;  - Use `git filter-branch` or `git-filter-repo` to remove from history

&#x20;  - \*\*Immediately rotate the JIRA token\*\* — the exposed token must be assumed compromised



2\. \*\*Add Missing 404 Tests\*\*

&#x20;  - Test `GET /health/{non-existent-id}` returns 404 with `HealthNotFoundError`

&#x20;  - Test `PUT /health/{non-existent-id}` returns 404 with proper error response

&#x20;  - Verify `DELETE /health/{non-existent-id}` returns 404



3\. \*\*Verify Test Fixture Async Handling\*\*

&#x20;  - Confirm conftest.py async session override works correctly with FastAPI's dependency system

&#x20;  - Consider using `AsyncClient` from httpx instead of manual async generator override



