\## Final Verdict



\*\*REQUEST CHANGES\*\* — Do not merge until:



1\. ✋ \*\*.env file removed\*\* and credentials rotated (security blocker)

2\. ✋ \*\*404 test cases added\*\* to meet coverage and specification requirements

3\. ✋ \*\*Test fixture verified\*\* to work correctly with FastAPI async dependencies



The architecture and code quality are \*\*excellent\*\*, but the security issue and test gaps are blocking. Once these three items are resolved, this PR should be \*\*APPROVED\*\*.

